Kristina Anapau https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kristina_Anapau 0 Kristina Elizabeth Anapau Roper (born October 30, 1979), better known as Kristina Anapau, is an American actress and writer. She is known for her roles as Maurella on the HBO series True Blood and as Galina in the 2010 film Black Swan.
